merging via the github UI doesnt support this anyway, which explains why noone else bothers with it.\r\nI'll still merge the PR in case thats fixed in the future and it will still help with local merges.\r\n\r\n* [x] Added an entry to `CHANGELOG.md` if knowledge of this change could be valuable to users\r\n* [x] Updated documentation to reflect any user-facing changes - in this repository\r\n* [x] Updated documentation to reflect any user-facing changes - PR to the [guide](https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano-www) that fixes existing documentation invalidated by this PR.\r\n", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1176/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1176/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1171", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1171/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1171/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1171/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1171", "id": 412243591, "node_id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0MjU0NDk4ODY2", "number": 1171, "title": "Fix image layout transitions", "user": {"login": "freesig", "id": 7286454, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjcyODY0NTQ=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/7286454?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/freesig", "html_url": "https://github.com/freesig", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/freesig/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/freesig/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/freesig/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/freesig/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/freesig/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/freesig/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/freesig/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/freesig/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/freesig/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 17, "created_at": "2019-02-20T04:46:00Z", "updated_at": "2019-05-19T23:35:17Z", "closed_at": "2019-05-19T12:56:15Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "type": null, "active_lock_reason": null, "draft": false, "pull_request": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pulls/1171", "html_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1171", "diff_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1171.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1171.patch", "merged_at": "2019-05-19T12:56:15Z"}, "body": "* [x] Added an entry to `CHANGELOG.md` if knowledge of this change could be valuable to users\r\n* [x] Updated documentation to reflect any user-facing changes - in this repository\r\n* [x] Updated documentation to reflect any user-facing changes - PR to the [guide](https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano-www) that fixes existing documentation invalidated by this PR.\r\n\r\nThis is another attempt at fixing the issues with layouts.\r\nSimilar to https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1117\r\nI've tested it with every example I currently have and haven't found any problems yet.\r\nHowever I would love some feedback because I'm relatively new to pipeline memory barriers.\r\n\r\nAll it really does is allow `AccessImage` to signal it has been initialized. For attachment images this means setting `initialized` to true and for swapchain images this mean setting `undefined_layout` to false.\r\n\r\nI signal it [here](https://github.com/freesig/vulkano/blob/1031ffbb1eef44d45c6aba63adc6820311ff4014/vulkano/src/command_buffer/synced/base.rs#L636) because if this condition is passed:\r\n```\r\n!self.is_secondary && resource_ty == KeyTy::Image &&\r\n                    start_layout != ImageLayout::Undefined &&\r\n                    start_layout != ImageLayout::Preinitialized\r\n```\r\nThen the image is either already transitioned out of undefined or a memory barrier is placed to do this transition.\r\nhttps://github.com/nannou-org/nannou/issues/271 is the issue that is tracking this work.", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1171/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1171/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1170", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1170/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1170/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1170/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1170", "id": 411435942, "node_id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0MjUzODg0NjEw", "number": 1170, "title": "Hash for Format", "user": {"login": "hikitrbogithub", "id": 46833698, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjQ2ODMzNjk4", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/46833698?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/hikitrbogithub", "html_url": "https://github.com/hikitrbogithub", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hikitrbogithub/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hikitrbogithub/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hikitrbogithub/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hikitrbogithub/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hikitrbogithub/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hikitrbogithub/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hikitrbogithub/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hikitrbogithub/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hikitrbogithub/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 1, "created_at": "2019-02-18T11:42:26Z", "updated_at": "2019-03-12T04:35:42Z", "closed_at": "2019-03-12T04:35:42Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "type": null, "active_lock_reason": null, "draft": false, "pull_request": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pulls/1170", "html_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1170", "diff_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1170.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1170.patch", "merged_at": "2019-03-12T04:35:41Z"}, "body": "Added derive Hash for Format\r\n\r\n* [ ] Added an entry to `CHANGELOG.md` if knowledge of this change could be valuable to users\r\n* [ ] Updated documentation to reflect any user-facing changes - in this repository\r\n* [ ] Updated documentation to reflect any user-facing changes - PR to the [guide](https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano-www) that fixes existing documentation invalidated by this PR.\r\n", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1170/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1170/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1166", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1166/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1166/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1166/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1166", "id": 407516666, "node_id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0MjUwOTczOTg5", "number": 1166, "title": "Fix compiler error in code generated for GLSL struct", "user": {"login": "mitchmindtree", "id": 4587373, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjQ1ODczNzM=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/4587373?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree", "html_url": "https://github.com/mitchmindtree", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 1, "created_at": "2019-02-07T02:22:55Z", "updated_at": "2019-02-07T02:55:25Z", "closed_at": "2019-02-07T02:55:25Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "type": null, "active_lock_reason": null, "draft": false, "pull_request": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pulls/1166", "html_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1166", "diff_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1166.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1166.patch", "merged_at": "2019-02-07T02:55:25Z"}, "body": "I was running into a compiler error generated by the `shader!` macro\r\nwhile writing a compute shader for a downstream commercial project.\r\nUsing `cargo-expand` I was able to find the generated code for the\r\nstruct and noticed that the current implementation would always generate\r\nan invalid type. *`{}` is never a valid length for a fixed size array of\r\nbytes.*\r\n\r\nIt seemed to me that `{}` was used within the `quote!` macro\r\naccidentally rather than `#diff` as this particular field is used to\r\nspecify a padding amount for matching the memory layout of the struct.\r\nBy changing the fixed size array len to use `#diff` I was able to\r\ncomplete compilation successfully and my code runs as expected.\r\n\r\n@tomaka can you confirm that this was likely a bug and that this is the\r\ncorrect fix? I want to check that this was not an intentional compile\r\nerror pending future work or a better error message.\r\n\r\n* [x] Added an entry to `CHANGELOG.md` if knowledge of this change could be valuable to users\r\n* [ ] ~Updated documentation to reflect any user-facing changes - in this repository~\r\n* [ ] ~Updated documentation to reflect any user-facing changes - PR to the [guide](https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano-www) that fixes existing documentation invalidated by this PR.~\r\n", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1166/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/i