": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pulls/1164", "html_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1164", "diff_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1164.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1164.patch", "merged_at": "2019-02-06T11:42:13Z"}, "body": "* [x] Added an entry to `CHANGELOG.md` if knowledge of this change could be valuable to users\r\n* [ ] Updated documentation to reflect any user-facing changes - in this repository\r\n* [ ] Updated documentation to reflect any user-facing changes - PR to the [guide](https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano-www) that fixes existing documentation invalidated by this PR.\r\n\r\nA small quality of life improvement.", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1164/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1164/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1163", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1163/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1163/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1163/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1163", "id": 406293351, "node_id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0MjUwMDIzNzAy", "number": 1163, "title": "Add an `instancing.rs` example.", "user": {"login": "mitchmindtree", "id": 4587373, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjQ1ODczNzM=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/4587373?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree", "html_url": "https://github.com/mitchmindtree", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mitchmindtree/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 3, "created_at": "2019-02-04T11:49:08Z", "updated_at": "2019-03-15T03:05:35Z", "closed_at": "2019-03-15T03:05:08Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "type": null, "active_lock_reason": null, "draft": false, "pull_request": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pulls/1163", "html_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1163", "diff_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1163.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1163.patch", "merged_at": "2019-03-15T03:05:08Z"}, "body": "This is a simple-as-possible example of how to do instancing with\r\nvulkano. The example is a direct copy of the `triangle.rs` example but\r\nremoves the comments in favour of only explaining the differences\r\nnecessary for doing instancing. Rather than drawing one triangle in the\r\ncentre of the screen, the example draws 100 instances of the triangle in\r\na 10x10 grid and get slightly larger across each axis.\r\n\r\nHere's a picture of what appears when running the example:\r\n\r\n![screenshot from 2019-02-04 22-38-15](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4587373/52206612-d8f7c000-28ce-11e9-8fa2-af75631f27fe.png)\r\n\r\nCloses #1162\r\n\r\n* [ ] ~~Added an entry to `CHANGELOG.md` if knowledge of this change could be valuable to users~~\r\n* [ ] ~Updated documentation to reflect any user-facing changes - in this repository~\r\n* [ ] ~Updated documentation to reflect any user-facing changes - PR to the [guide](https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano-www) that fixes existing documentation invalidated by this PR.~\r\n", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1163/reactions", "total_count": 1, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 1, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1163/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1161", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1161/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1161/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/vulkano-rs/vulkano/issues/1161/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/vulkano-rs/vulkano/pull/1161", "id": 405390122, "node_id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0MjQ5MzYxMTQz", "number": 1161, "title": "Make buffer::sys::UnsafeBuffer::new panic if the usage parameter is empty", "user": {"login": "shuni64", "id": 28684831, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI4Njg0ODMx", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/28684831?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/shuni64", "html_url": "https://github.com/shuni64", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/shuni64/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/shuni64/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/shuni64/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/shuni64/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https: